      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AELIANA (4) finds her race third-up. Finished second to Autumn Glow in the G2 Apollo and then ran a slashing second in the G1 Verry Elleegant (Chipping Norton) Stakes over 1600m at Randwick. No Autumn Glow today and has the fitness edge over the bulk of these. SIR DELIUS (1) Multiple Group 1 winner who excels over this trip. Knocked up in the straight first-up when third over 1600m in the G1 Verry Elleegant Stakes at Randwick. Expected to have come on strongly but doubt he can turn the tables. LINDERMANN (2) saves his best for this track and trip and can return to form after pulling up with cardiac arrhythmia when last in the Verry Elleegant. Has never missed the frame here at this journey in four starts. Minor place contender. ALALCANCE (6) good tough staying mare who will roll forward after finishing a close-up sixth when resuming over 2000m in the LR Randwick City Stakes. Adept in all conditions and can sneak into the minor money.",
